From {{inh|en|enm|abissus}}, from {{der|en|LL.|abyssus||a bottomless gulf}}, from {{der|en|grc|ἄβυσσος||bottomless}}, from {{m|grc|ἀ-||not}} + {{m|grc|βυσσός||deep place}},<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref><ref name=AHD>{{R:American Heritage Dictionary|edition=1971|page=6}}</ref> from {{m|grc|βυθός||deep place}}.<ref name=WI3>{{R:MW3 1976|page=9}}</ref>

